Baluchistan (Gwadar). 2 Dec 2016. In Gwadar, hundreds of people have been reportedly hospitalized due to the contagious virus, and then there are reported deaths. The Government of Balochistan needs to take concrete steps for the safe recovery of the people from this dangerous and deadly disease.
http://pakobserver.net/dengue-virus-in-gwadar/

